{"id": "4085", "post": "<div class=\"post-4085 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-virtual-servers tag-dallas tag-shardhost-com tag-texas\" id=\"post-4085\"><h2 class=\"storytitle\"><a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/blog/shardhost-30year-1024mb-kvm-in-dallas-texas/\" rel=\"bookmark\">ShardHost \u2013 $30/Year 1024MB KVM in Dallas, Texas</a></h2><div class=\"meta\"><img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"/media/icons/tag_green.png\" data-src=\"/media/icons/tag_green.png\" alt=\"Tags: \" class=\"litespeed-loaded\" data-was-processed=\"true\"> <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/dallas/\" rel=\"tag\">dallas</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/shardhost-com/\" rel=\"tag\">shardhost.com</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/texas/\" rel=\"tag\">texas</a> <img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"https://lowendbox.com/media/icons/calendar.png\" data-src=\"https://lowendbox.com/media/icons/calendar.png\" alt=\"Date/Time: \" class=\"litespeed-loaded\" data-was-processed=\"true\"> July 13, 2013 @ 10:22 pm, by Liam</div><div class=\"storycontent tablelook\"><p><a href=\"http://www.shardhost.com\" target=\"_blank\"><img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/shardhost.jpg.webp\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"screenshot litespeed-loaded\" title=\"ShardHost\" alt=\"\" data-src=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/shardhost.jpg.webp\" width=\"300\" height=\"190\" data-was-processed=\"true\"></a>Marc, from <a href=\"http://www.shardhost.com\">ShardHost</a>, has sent in four annual/monthly offers to celebrate their second birthday. Whilst there are only three offers shown below, you can see the fourth offer by clicking \u2018more\u2019.</p><table><tbody><tr><td valign=\"top\"><strong>1024mb KVM</strong><p></p><ul><li>1024MB RAM</li><li>1024MB Swap</li><li>3 vCPU Cores</li><li>100GB Diskspace</li><li>1024GB Bandwidth</li><li>KVM/SolusVM</li><li>1 IPv4 Address</li><li>$5/Month | <a href=\"https://my.shardhost.com/cart.php?a=add&amp;pid=25\">Order</a></li></ul></td><td valign=\"top\"><strong>256mb KVM</strong><p></p><ul><li>256MB RAM</li><li>256MB Swap</li><li>1 vCPU Core</li><li>5GB Diskspace</li><li>256GB Bandwidth</li><li>KVM/SolusVM</li><li>1 IPv4 Address</li><li>$10/Year | <a href=\"https://my.shardhost.com/cart.php?a=add&amp;pid=21\">Order</a></li></ul></td><td valign=\"top\"><strong>1024mb KVM</strong><p></p><ul><li>1024MB RAM</li><li>1024MB Swap</li><li>2 vCPU Cores</li><li>20GB Diskspace</li><li>1024GB Bandwidth</li><li>KVM/SolusVM</li><li>1 IPv4 Address</li><li>$30/Year | <a href=\"https://my.shardhost.com/cart.php?a=add&amp;pid=23\">Order</a></li></ul></td></tr></tbody></table><p>ShardHost is a UK LTD company (reg 07679837) that has been providing hosting services since June 2011. We have featured them <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/blog/shardhost-7month-1024mb-kvm-2048mb-openvz-in-dallas-texas/\">once before</a> on LowEndBox. They currently serve over 3500 clients on their fully owned vps hardware. Their SuperMicro servers are running Intel Xeon E3 1240 v1/v2 processors, Enterprise Hard Drives (WD RE4 or Seagate Constellations) with hardware Raid 10. Marc informs us that they can \u201cdouble/triple resources on any plan for double/triple the price\u201d. Reviews on their previous thread, as well as on let <a href=\"http://www.lowendtalk.com/discussion/8936/shardhost-review\">1</a> <a href=\"http://www.lowendtalk.com/discussion/9418/shardhost-review\">2</a> <a href=\"http://www.lowendtalk.com/discussion/9367/best-vps-i-ever-had-shardhost\">3</a>, all seem to be positive.<br>\n<span id=\"more-4085\"></span></p><table><tbody><tr><td valign=\"top\"><strong>512mb KVM</strong><p></p><ul><li>512MB RAM</li><li>512MB Swap</li><li>1 vCPU Cores</li><li>10GB Diskspace</li><li>512GB Bandwidth</li><li>KVM/SolusVM</li><li>1 IPv4 Address</li><li>$18/Year | <a href=\"https://my.shardhost.com/cart.php?a=add&amp;pid=22\">Order Now</a></li></ul></td></tr></tbody></table><p>ShardHost currently only accept Paypal. They offer a 7 day moneyback guarantee. EU clients will be liable for VAT charged @ 20% (GB136446902). Plans come with one IPv4, additional IPv4 are $1/mo. IPv6 is not currently available. To summarise their Terms of Service: Be a good neighbour, No spam/abuse, Legal stored content only and finally No TOR. For more information, have a read of their <a href=\"http://www.shardhost.com/tos.php\">Terms of Service</a> and their <a href=\"http://www.shardhost.com/aup.php\">Acceptable Usage Policy</a>.</p><p><strong>Network Information:</strong></p><p>Servers are located at the Colo4Dallas datacenter (via ColoCrossing) in Dallas, Texas.</p><p>Test IPv4: 172.245.61.2<br>\nTest Files: <a href=\"http://172.245.61.2/10mb.bin\">10mb</a> &amp; <a href=\"http://172.245.61.2/100mb.bin\">100mb</a></p><p class=\"dpsp-share-text\"></p><div id=\"dpsp-content-bottom\" class=\"dpsp-content-wrapper dpsp-shape-rounded dpsp-column-auto dpsp-has-spacing dpsp-no-labels dpsp-show-on-mobile dpsp-button-style-1 dpsp-has-icon-background dpsp-has-button-background dpsp-show-total-share-count dpsp-show-total-share-count-after\"><ul class=\"dpsp-networks-btns-wrapper dpsp-networks-btns-content dpsp-has-button-icon-animation\"><li><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/sharer/sharer.php?u=https%3A%2F%2Flowendbox.com%2Fblog%2Fshardhost-30year-1024mb-kvm-in-dallas-texas%2F&amp;t=ShardHost%20-%20%2430%2FYear%201024MB%20KVM%20in%20Dallas%2C%20Texas\" class=\"dpsp-network-btn dpsp-facebook dpsp-no-label dpsp-first\" title=\"Share on Facebook\"><span class=\"dpsp-network-icon\"></span><span class=\"dpsp-network-label-wrapper\"></span></a></li><li><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?text=ShardHost%20-%20%2430%2FYear%201024MB%20KVM%20in%20Dallas%2C%20Texas&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Flowendbox.com%2Fblog%2Fshardhost-30year-1024mb-kvm-in-dallas-texas%2F&amp;via=LowEndNetwork\" class=\"dpsp-network-btn dpsp-twitter dpsp-no-label\" title=\"Share on Twitter